{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/docker/git和容器-cicd/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"升高"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4026c619-4139-5aee-a17f-f219bee12c2f","excerpt":"1 自动化流程 自动化构建和提交镜像\n 自动化部署\n 2 自动化流程 2.1 github actions github action 文档地址 2.2 使用 github action 自动构建镜像并上传到 dockerhub 中 项目地址 https://github.com/shenggaowei/docker…","html":"<h2>1 自动化流程</h2>\n<p>自动化构建和提交镜像\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/edd86c32c5a1dc982c2896b41ae41d0e/8deec/dev-ops.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"dev-ops.png\"\n        title=\"dev-ops.png\"\n        src=\"/static/edd86c32c5a1dc982c2896b41ae41d0e/f058b/dev-ops.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/edd86c32c5a1dc982c2896b41ae41d0e/c26ae/dev-ops.png 158w,\n/static/edd86c32c5a1dc982c2896b41ae41d0e/6bdcf/dev-ops.png 315w,\n/static/edd86c32c5a1dc982c2896b41ae41d0e/f058b/dev-ops.png 630w,\n/static/edd86c32c5a1dc982c2896b41ae41d0e/40601/dev-ops.png 945w,\n/static/edd86c32c5a1dc982c2896b41ae41d0e/78612/dev-ops.png 1260w,\n/static/edd86c32c5a1dc982c2896b41ae41d0e/8deec/dev-ops.png 2136w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>自动化部署\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4a15c4fcdae553388b933f32c5d80d1c/dec58/dev-ops2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.75949367088608%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"dev-ops2.png\"\n        title=\"dev-ops2.png\"\n        src=\"/static/4a15c4fcdae553388b933f32c5d80d1c/f058b/dev-ops2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4a15c4fcdae553388b933f32c5d80d1c/c26ae/dev-ops2.png 158w,\n/static/4a15c4fcdae553388b933f32c5d80d1c/6bdcf/dev-ops2.png 315w,\n/static/4a15c4fcdae553388b933f32c5d80d1c/f058b/dev-ops2.png 630w,\n/static/4a15c4fcdae553388b933f32c5d80d1c/40601/dev-ops2.png 945w,\n/static/4a15c4fcdae553388b933f32c5d80d1c/78612/dev-ops2.png 1260w,\n/static/4a15c4fcdae553388b933f32c5d80d1c/dec58/dev-ops2.png 2133w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>2 自动化流程</h2>\n<h3>2.1 github actions</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/zh/actions\">github action 文档地址</a></p>\n<h3>2.2 使用 github action 自动构建镜像并上传到 dockerhub 中</h3>\n<p>项目地址 <a href=\"https://github.com/shenggaowei/docker-start\">https://github.com/shenggaowei/docker-start</a></p>\n<p>在项目 .github/workflows 下创建 docker-build.yml 文件</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yml\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Docker image build and push\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>push<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">jobs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">Docker-Build-Push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">runs-on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ubuntu<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>latest\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">steps</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Check out repository code\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> actions/checkout@v2\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker image build\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker image build <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>t shenggao/flask<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>demo<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>latest .\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> list docker image\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker image ls\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> dockerhub login\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker login <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>u $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.DOCKERHUB_USERNAME <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>p $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.DOCKERHUB_PASSWORD <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> push to dockerhub\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker image push shenggao/flask<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>demo<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>latest</code></pre></div>\n<p>在 <a href=\"https://hub.docker.com/settings/security\">dockerhub 网站</a> 申请 access-token 代替密码。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6437d5e1075aa226d6d15f710958d2d5/52fbd/access-token.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.734177215189874%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"docker-hub-access-token.png\"\n        title=\"docker-hub-access-token.png\"\n        src=\"/static/6437d5e1075aa226d6d15f710958d2d5/f058b/access-token.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6437d5e1075aa226d6d15f710958d2d5/c26ae/access-token.png 158w,\n/static/6437d5e1075aa226d6d15f710958d2d5/6bdcf/access-token.png 315w,\n/static/6437d5e1075aa226d6d15f710958d2d5/f058b/access-token.png 630w,\n/static/6437d5e1075aa226d6d15f710958d2d5/40601/access-token.png 945w,\n/static/6437d5e1075aa226d6d15f710958d2d5/78612/access-token.png 1260w,\n/static/6437d5e1075aa226d6d15f710958d2d5/52fbd/access-token.png 3124w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>在 github 项目的 settings -> secrets 中将 dockerhub 的用户名和 access-token 填进去。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d6486809a5179e50f9796582438f8786/de720/github-secrets.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"github-secrets.png\"\n        title=\"github-secrets.png\"\n        src=\"/static/d6486809a5179e50f9796582438f8786/f058b/github-secrets.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d6486809a5179e50f9796582438f8786/c26ae/github-secrets.png 158w,\n/static/d6486809a5179e50f9796582438f8786/6bdcf/github-secrets.png 315w,\n/static/d6486809a5179e50f9796582438f8786/f058b/github-secrets.png 630w,\n/static/d6486809a5179e50f9796582438f8786/40601/github-secrets.png 945w,\n/static/d6486809a5179e50f9796582438f8786/78612/github-secrets.png 1260w,\n/static/d6486809a5179e50f9796582438f8786/de720/github-secrets.png 3452w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>push 代码，可在 actions 中看到自动构建的效果。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/505b7225307d306f9dec0885a7338462/e843c/github-actions-ret1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"github-actions-ret1.png\"\n        title=\"github-actions-ret1.png\"\n        src=\"/static/505b7225307d306f9dec0885a7338462/f058b/github-actions-ret1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/505b7225307d306f9dec0885a7338462/c26ae/github-actions-ret1.png 158w,\n/static/505b7225307d306f9dec0885a7338462/6bdcf/github-actions-ret1.png 315w,\n/static/505b7225307d306f9dec0885a7338462/f058b/github-actions-ret1.png 630w,\n/static/505b7225307d306f9dec0885a7338462/40601/github-actions-ret1.png 945w,\n/static/505b7225307d306f9dec0885a7338462/78612/github-actions-ret1.png 1260w,\n/static/505b7225307d306f9dec0885a7338462/e843c/github-actions-ret1.png 3890w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>同时登陆 dockerhub，镜像已经被推送上去。</p>\n<h3>2.3 使用 buildx 方式构建多架构版本的镜像</h3>\n<p>修改 yml 文件</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yml\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Docker image build and push\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>push<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">jobs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">Docker-Build-Push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">runs-on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ubuntu<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>latest\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">steps</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Check out repository code\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> actions/checkout@v2\n\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Set up QEMU\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker/setup<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>qemu<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>action@v2\n\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Set up Docker Buildx\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> buildx\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker/setup<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>buildx<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>action@v2\n\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Avaliable platforms\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> echo $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> steps.buildx.outputs.platforms <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> build and push\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token scalar string\">\n          docker login -u ${{ secrets.DOCKERHUB_USERNAME }} -p ${{ secrets.DOCKERHUB_PASSWORD }}\n          docker buildx ls\n          docker buildx build --push --platform linux/arm/v7,linux/arm64/v8,linux/amd64 -t shenggao/flask-demo:latest .</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>使用 QEMU action 添加在 ubuntu 中 docker 所缺失的模拟环境（具体是啥需要再去研究）。使用 buildx action 配置 buildx 环境，能够使用 buildx 进行构建。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/marketplace/actions/docker-setup-buildx\">https://github.com/marketplace/actions/docker-setup-buildx</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/marketplace/actions/docker-setup-qemu\">https://github.com/marketplace/actions/docker-setup-qemu</a></p>\n<h3>2.4 使用 build and push docker images 进一步简化流程</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/marketplace/actions/build-and-push-docker-images\">https://github.com/marketplace/actions/build-and-push-docker-images</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yml\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Docker image build and push\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>push<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">jobs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">Docker-Build-Push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">runs-on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ubuntu<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>latest\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">steps</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Check out repository code\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> actions/checkout@v2\n\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Set up QEMU\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker/setup<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>qemu<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>action@v2\n\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Set up Docker Buildx\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> buildx\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker/setup<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>buildx<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>action@v2\n\t\t\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Avaliable platforms\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> echo $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> steps.buildx.outputs.platforms <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Login to Docker Hub\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker/login<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>action@v2\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">with</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">username</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.DOCKERHUB_USERNAME <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">password</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.DOCKERHUB_PASSWORD <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Build and push\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> docker/build<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>push<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>action@v3\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">with</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span>\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">platforms</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> linux/arm/v7<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>linux/arm64/v8<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>linux/amd64\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">tags</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> shenggao/flask<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>demo<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>latest</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"11 git和容器-cicd","date":"December 26, 2022","description":"docker 学习笔记"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/docker/asset/docker多架构支持/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"10 Docker学习之docker多架构支持"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"4026c619-4139-5aee-a17f-f219bee12c2f","previousPostId":"48c0cc29-652e-584c-8d27-5bad78f1c4e4","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"]}